↓
[L1 - Initial Response & Triage]
↓
[Can L1 Resolve?] → Yes → [Document & Close]
↓ No
[L2 - Technical Investigation]
↓
[Can L2 Resolve?] → Yes → [Document & Close]
↓ No
[L3 - Expert Intervention]
↓
[Can L3 Resolve?] → Yes → [Document & Close]
↓ No
[L4 - Management Escalation][Incident Detected]
↓
[L1 - Initial Response & Triage]
↓
