## Escalation Communication Template

**Subject**: ESCALATION - [Severity] - [Brief Description]

**Incident Details**:
- Incident ID: [ID]
- Severity: [P1/P2/P3/P4]
- Started: [Date/Time]
- Duration: [Hours]

**Current Status**: [Brief update]

**Reason for Escalation**: [Why escalating]

**Action Required**: [What you need from the escalation point]

**Business Impact**: [User/revenue impact]
